        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Target your pet /pet kill mob(whatever the mob is)</P><P>It will attack the first one that comes into aggro range of him, but thats all.  He will not continue to attack others, you will have to reissue the command each time.  Unless there is another way, but I was never able to do it with out reissuing the commands.  I made a hot key titled</P><P>Farm<BR>/pet kill a decaying</P><P>I go into the newbie area in Paineel and keep mashing it over and over and pick up all the dead bodies.</P><P>Hope this helps</P><P>Azerzen D'Malocchio<BR>Mystic Aura<BR>Terris-Thule<BR><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Profile=0&Id=69349" target="_blank">http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Profile=0&Id=69349</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
